Hello,

Your  patience has truly been appreciated. A known issue was preventing shipping labels from being printed from the USPS by Endicia shipping module when letters were present in the store phone number in Setup and Tools > Profile. We are pleased to announce this has been resolved so that now letters can be included in store phone numbers without interfering with shipping labels.

Please don't hesitate to contact us 24hrs a day if you have any other questions or concerns: https://support.bigcommerce.com/contact.php

